HEADWORD: Prognosticator
<hw>Prog*nos"ti*ca`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
prognosticates; a foreknower or foreteller of a future course or event
by present signs.</def> <rj><au>Isa. xlvii. 13.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

